==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ultimo
<hw>Ul"ti*mo</hw>. <ety>[L. <ets>ultimo</ets> (<ets>mense</ets>) in
the last month.]</ety> <def>In the month immediately preceding the
present; <as>as, on the 1st <ex>ultimo</ex></as>; -- usually abbreviated
to <abbr>ult.</abbr> Cf. <er>Proximo</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ultion</ent>⟦br⟧
